        </li>
        <li>
            <span class="contact-label">GitHub Repository:</span>
            <a class="contact-link" href="https://github.com/DwaineDGIlmer" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
                https://github.com/DwaineDGIlmer
            </a>
        </li>
        <li>
            <span class="contact-label">Azure Web App:</span>
